Fatin Abdel Wahab (22 Nọvemba 1913 - 12 Mee 1972) bụ onye nduzi ihe nkiri Ijipt
O duziri ihe nkiri ịrị ise na abụọ n'agbata afọ 1949 na 1970

E tinyere ihe nkiri ya nke 1961 a kpọrọ Wife Number 13 n'ime 12th Berlin International Film Festival. E tinyere ihe nkiri ya nke 1965 Driven from Paradise n'ime 4th Moscow International Film Festival.
